CFBD Ratings and Rankings Endpoints

cfbd_ratings.Rd

Postseason polls are after Week 13

At least one of year or team must be specified for the function to run

At least one of year or team must be specified for the function to run

cfbd_rankings(year, week = NULL, season_type = "regular", verbose = FALSE)

cfbd_ratings_sp(year = NULL, team = NULL, verbose = FALSE)

cfbd_ratings_sp_conference(year = NULL, conference = NULL, verbose = FALSE)

cfbd_ratings_srs(year = NULL, team = NULL, conference = NULL, verbose = FALSE)

Arguments

year

(Integer optional): Year, 4 digit format (YYYY)
week

(Integer optional): Week, values from 1-15, 1-14 for seasons pre-playoff (i.e. 2013 or earlier)
season_type

(String default regular): Season type - regular or postseason
verbose

Logical parameter (TRUE/FALSE, default: FALSE) to return warnings and messages from function
team

(String optional): D-I Team
conference

(String optional): Conference abbreviation - SRS information by conference
Conference abbreviations P5: ACC, B12, B1G, SEC, PAC
Conference abbreviations G5 and FBS Independents: CUSA, MAC, MWC, Ind, SBC, AAC

Source

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/rankings

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/ratings/sp

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/ratings/sp/conferences

https://api.collegefootballdata.com/ratings/srs
